<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <title>Welcome to MySpeak+</title>
  <style>
    body {
      background-color:rgb(221, 249, 255);
      font-family: 'Lato', sans-serif;
      font-size: 16px;
      margin: 0;
      padding: 30px;
      color: #333;
    }
    .container {
      background-color: #ffffff;
      max-width: 600px;
      margin: auto;
      padding: 30px;
      border-radius: 12px;
      box-shadow: 0 4px 10px rgba(0,0,0,0.05);
    }
    .header {
      font-size: 26px;
      font-weight: bold;
      margin-bottom: 10px;
      text-align: center;
      color: #222;
    }
    .subheader {
      font-size: 16px;
      color: #666;
      text-align: center;
      margin-bottom: 30px;
    }
    .content {
      font-size: 16px;
      line-height: 1.6;
    }
    .button {
      display: inline-block;
      background-color: #28a745;
      color: white;
      text-decoration: none;
      padding: 12px 24px;
      border-radius: 6px;
      font-weight: 600;
      font-size: 16px;
      margin-top: 20px;
    }
    .footer {
      font-size: 14px;
      color: #888;
      margin-top: 40px;
      text-align: center;
    }
    a {
      color: #007bff;
      text-decoration: none;
    }
    ul {
      padding-left: 20px;
      margin-top: 10px;
      list-style-type: none;
      text-align: left;
    }
    .lead-text {
      font-weight: bold;
      margin-top: 20px;
      margin-bottom: 10px;
      margin-left: 20px;
      font-size: 18px;
      text-align: left;
      line-height: 1.4;
      color: #333;
    }
    .secondary-text {
      font-size: 16px;
      font-weight: 600;
      color: #555;
      margin-top: 20px;
      margin-bottom: 20px;
      text-align: center;
    }
    .signature {
      margin-top: 30px;
      font-style: italic;
      color: #555;
      text-align: center;
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="container">
    <div class="header">Welcome to MySpeak+</div>
    <div class="subheader">You're all set—let's make your voice heard.</div>

    <div class="content">
      <p>Hi <%= @user.name.blank? ? "there" : @user.name %>,</p>

      <p>Thank you for upgrading to <strong>MySpeak+</strong>! </p>
      <p>Your personalized page is now ready to be set up.</p>

      <p class="lead-text">As a MySpeak+ member, you can:</p>
      <ul>
        <li>✅ Create a scannable profile with emergency contact (ICE) info</li>
        <li>✅ Add key medical and safety details</li>
        <li>✅ Help first responders, caregivers, and loved ones support you faster</li>
      </ul>

      <p class="secondary-text">All of this lives behind your own QR code! <br>Simple, shareable, and always available.</p>

      <p style="text-align: center;">
        <a href="<%= @login_link %>" class="button">Claim Your MySpeak Page</a>
      </p>

      <p>Once you've set it up, you can always access your page <a href="<%= @mymyspeak_link %>" target="_blank">here</a>.</p>

      <p>Need help or have questions? Just reply to this email or reach out to <a href="mailto:help@speakanyway.com">help@speakanyway.com</a> — we've got your back.</p>

      <p>Thanks again for supporting SpeakAnyWay.<br>We're so glad you're here.</p>

      <p class="signature">
      Warmly,<br>The SpeakAnyWay Team</p>
    </div>

    <div class="footer">
      You're receiving this email because you signed up for MySpeak+.<br>
      Want to manage your subscription? Visit your account settings.
    </div>
  </div>
</body>
</html>
